Mar 5, 2025
GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF NORTH CAROLINA
S.B. 236
SESSION 2025
PRINCIPAL CLERK
S D
SENATE BILL DRS45122-LGa-79
Short Title: Funds for Edgecombe CC. (Public)
Sponsors: Senator Smith (Primary Sponsor).
Referred to:
1 A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
2 AN ACT TO APPROPRIATE FUNDS TO EDGECOMBE COMMUNITY COLLEGE FOR
3 CONSTRUCTION OF THE INDUSTRIAL TECHNOLOGY AND SKILLED TRADES
4 FACILITY.
5 The General Assembly of North Carolina enacts:
6 SECTION 1. There is appropriated from the General Fund to the Office of State
7 Budget and Management the sum of one million dollars ($1,000,000) in nonrecurring funds for
8 the 2025-2026 fiscal year to provide a directed grant to Edgecombe Community College for the
9 construction of the Industrial Technology and Skilled Trades Facility, which will aid the College
10 in strengthening the area's workforce.
11 SECTION 2. This act becomes effective July 1, 2025.
*DRS45122-LGa-79*

